In this task, we created a robot control panel on web page utilizing html and php languages and XAMPP software. 
A database was created on XAMPP software. 
By the use of index.html file, the control panel page was formated with four dirction buttons and an extra stop button was addtionally included. 
connect.php and view.php files were used to make connection between the control panel web page and the database to insert and retrieve data to and from the database. 
